Introduction

Youngseo is a South Korean idol trainee formely under Belift Lab. In 2023, she participated in the survival show R U Next?, where she ranked second and was chosen to debut in the group ILLIT.

On January 4, 2024, Youngseo left ILLIT after coming to a mutual agreement to terminate her contract with Belift Lab.
